<span id="freeTextContainer10879355553070365660">I read this for my Intro to Gender and Women&apos;s studies course and I absolutely loved it. <br/><br/>It&apos;s the perfect place to start if you&apos;re interested in diving into feminist studies or even if you&apos;re already well versed in the subject. It really is for EVERYBODY (pun very much intended). </span>
  <span id="freeText10879355553070365660" style="display:none">I read this for my Intro to Gender and Women's studies course and I absolutely loved it. <br /><br />It's the perfect place to start if you're interested in diving into feminist studies or even if you're already well versed in the subject. It really is for EVERYBODY (pun very much intended). </span>
